Description: Fix CVE-2024-29857 - F2m curve field size bounds check
 Importing an EC certificate with crafted F2m parameters can lead to
 excessive CPU consumption. Adds a maximum bounds check on F2m field size
 (m) in ECCurve.F2m.buildField, configurable via
 org.bouncycastle.ec.max_f2m_field_size (default 1142). Also backports
 Properties.asInteger() required by the upstream fix API (not present in
 1.70). Adapted from upstream commits efc498c / fee80dd for r1rv70's
 buildField implementation.
Origin: upstream, https://github.com/bcgit/bc-java/commit/fee80dd230e7fba132d03a34f1dd1d6aae0d0281
Bug: https://github.com/bcgit/bc-java/wiki/CVE%E2%80%902024%E2%80%9029857
Last-Update: 2026-07-17

