Description: Fix CVE-2025-8916 - cap SubjectAltName size in PKIXCertPathReviewer
 PKIXCertPathReviewer lacked a limit on Subject Alternative Name entries
 processed during name-constraint checks, enabling DoS via oversized SAN
 extensions. Adds NAME_CHECK_MAX (1024) matching upstream. Only the
 deprecated prov x509 reviewer exists in 1.70 (pkix jcajce class was
 introduced later); that is the applicable fix surface for this version.
Origin: upstream, https://github.com/bcgit/bc-java/commit/ff444a479942d88de64004dc82c3ee32a9e9075a
Bug: https://github.com/bcgit/bc-java/wiki/CVE%E2%80%902025%E2%80%908916
Last-Update: 2026-07-17

